{"tid":12370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（申請法緩）11名旺角暴動被告涉十四項罪名案件押後至下月17日再審","createTime":"2016-11-29T15:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T16:44:31.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d4b1e175f60fb835321e94cc81ef974289d16c2","tid":12370,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:29:14.000Z","msg":"十一名在大年初一晚旺角騷亂案中, 被控共十四項暴動、 刑事損壞、 襲擊致造成身體傷害和襲警的被告, 再在區域法院提訊. 各人准以原有條件繼續保釋. 由於控辯雙方都需要時間交收案中相關錄影片段, 因此案件會押後至明年一月十七日再提訊.<br />\n        控方指可在一星期內將涉案的幾百小時錄影片段轉交各被告, 但他們需要時間與律師商討, 因此申請押後, 其中一名被告今天沒有代表律師, 他指正申請法律援助, 法援處指如果他按時交齊申請文件, 可在三星期內完成審批, 法官指今次是最後一次押後提訊, 提醒他要在這段期間處理好法援申請. 法官又預計案件聆訊會排期在暑假期間進行, 提醒各被告代表律師要預留時間.<br />\n        十男一女被告年齡介乎十七到七十歲, 控罪指他們於今年二月九日在旺角參與暴動、 襲擊警員和刑事損壞警車等罪名. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20161129154806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20161129154806&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=1def7f90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20161129154806</a><br />\n本民前說好的法律支援呢，衰到要自己申請法緩打官司，又無保險，又無安家費，入到罪後前途盡毀，你玩埋去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0b7679cd933d7b16b07f94a94ee49a756cab27","tid":12370,"uid":34029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"一句義士 坐唔知幾多年 咩前途都冇灑 雖然自己都係做唔到d咩 但香港人太自私太狗"},{"pid":"5ffdf16b643df89b5326cf2585d1ee5dd3beccb6","tid":12370,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"每人坐返兩年，出返來再做旗子衝過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df18d202fc6fabf18ef465d713c343e7369c3fc2","tid":12370,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 光之練金術師 )"},{"pid":"b391abeba99fbf7a86e16dc5ece5e03d0b97830c","tid":12370,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:42:28.000Z","msg":"大家記著保持陣形向前衝，等班大佬輩可以殿後"},{"pid":"ea2a602c800a95575431faaf9ce4ccc4eec9f135","tid":12370,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:42:59.000Z","msg":"隻五毛跟到埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966ef78ff7650c89025416985c7a9fa368d43077","tid":12370,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:44:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻五毛跟到埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個？"},{"pid":"f963f493357dbf1c64fe3c78c1bb59f7162c2d5b","tid":12370,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隻五毛跟到埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個？</blockquote><br />\n樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865da6d6314449f011f442d64c5a131252f7bfa2","tid":12370,"uid":4722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:44:31.000Z","msg":"梁天琦暴動罪成慶祝區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}